item.title: An analysis of last year's PB survey
item.description: Introduction This report is a preliminary analysis of the Queens College survey data. The report is divided into the following sections I. Overview of data and concerns II. Prelimnary summary statistics III. Possible Future explorations. I. Data Overview As with most surveys, the data is fairly messy in particular there are lots of missing values across the varibales and there are various ways that can be dealt with.
